formattedQuery: SELECT $timeSeries as t, count() FROM $table WHERE $timeFilter GROUP BY t ORDER BY t
query: SELECT $timeSeries as t, avg(load_in) as Admiral_Bellman FROM $table WHERE managed_object = 6236587862505104878 and path[4]=toString('Te 0/0/0') and $timeFilter GROUP BY t ORDER BY t
rawQuery: SELECT (intDiv(toUInt32(ts), 20) * 20) * 1000 as t, avg(load_in) as Admiral_Bellman FROM noc.interface WHERE managed_object = 6236587862505104878 and path[4]=toString('Te 0/0/0') and date >= toDate(1702951658) AND date <= toDate(1702973258) AND ts >= toDateTime(1702951658) AND ts <= toDateTime(1702973258) GROUP BY t ORDER BY t
